  {
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "id": "TALK_JOHN",
    "dynamic_line": "&[As you walk up to the counter, you can see someone cleaning a glass w/ a spitrag.] \n\n \"Howdy, the name's John. I'm the owner of this fine establishment, and I'm sellin' Gas 'n Alcohol. Want some?\"",
    "responses": [
      { "text": "I'll have some fuel for me, & fuel for my car.", "effect": "start_trade", "topic": "TALK_JOHN" },
      { "text": "Do you have any family?", "topic": "TALK_JOHN_FAMILY" },
      { "text": "What's that red shirt you're wearin' under that dress shirt?", "topic": "TALK_JOHN_MAGA" },
      { "text": "[Leave] \"No thanks sir.\"", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ],
    "replace_built_in_responses": true
  },
  {
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "id": "TALK_JOHN_AFTER_ANGER",
    "dynamic_line": "&[He lowers his shotgun.] \n\n \"Alright. Despite your lack of respect, I'm still willing to trade with you.\"",
    "responses": [
      { "text": "I'll have some fuel for me, & fuel for my car.", "effect": "start_trade", "topic": "TALK_JOHN" },
      { "text": "[Leave] \"I'll just... go \"", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ],
    "replace_built_in_responses": true
  },
  {
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "id": "TALK_JOHN_FAMILY",
    "dynamic_line": "&[He looks you up and down.] \n\n \"Well, it was just me and Dora for a long time. I always wanted kids y'know, someone to raise and to teach. I tried and succeeded with Dora, but...\" \n\n[He stares down into the glass he was cleaning just a few seconds earlier.]",
    "responses": [
      { "text": "But what?.", "topic": "TALK_JOHN_FAMILY_A" },
      { "text": "I'm sorry for your loss...", "topic": "TALK_JOHN_FAMILY_B" },
      { "text": "[Leave in the middle of the dammed conversation.]", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ],
    "replace_built_in_responses": true
  },
  {
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "id": "TALK_JOHN_FAMILY_A",
    "dynamic_line": "&[He looks back up towards you.] \n\n \"She... Had a miscarriage not long after the Cataclysm. When her water broke, there was no doctor arround; Dennis hadn't shown up yet, and I wasn't skilled enough to do it. Baby died, turned into a bloody mess, thankfully Dora survived. She's upstairs in a coma. When Dennis finally arrived sh- *he* did a checkup on her, claims that she's stable, but in a deep coma. She'll wake up though, I know she will.\" \n \"She's tough like that.\"",
    "responses": [
      { "text": "I'm sorry to hear that..", "topic": "TALK_JOHN" },
      {
        "text": "Are you sure she'll wake up? It sounds like she's in there pretty deep.",
        "topic": "TALK_JOHN_FAMILY_A_ANGER"
      },
      { "text": "[Leave]", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ],
    "replace_built_in_responses": true
  },
  {
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "id": "TALK_JOHN_FAMILY_A_ANGER",
    "dynamic_line": "&[He scowls at you.] \n\n \"Take that back you SONOFABITCH!\"\n\n[You can see both barrels of his shotgun pointed square at your chest.]",
    "responses": [
      { "text": "I take it back! I take it back!", "topic": "TALK_JOHN_AFTER_ANGER" },
      {
        "text": "I don't think she'll wake up at all! In fact, you're a crazy old man!",
        "effect": "hostile",
        "topic": "TALK_DONE"
      },
      { "text": "[RUN!]", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ],
    "replace_built_in_responses": true
  },
  {
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "id": "TALK_JOHN_FAMILY_B",
    "dynamic_line": "&[He looks back up sharply.] \n\n \"What!? No! She ain't dead, she's sleepin' upstairs!\"",
    "responses": [
      { "text": "Oh, I'm sorry. What happened?", "topic": "TALK_JOHN_A" },
      { "text": "I-Just... Nevermind.", "topic": "TALK_JOHN" },
      { "text": "[Leave] \"Sorry...\"", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ],
    "replace_built_in_responses": true
  },
  {
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "id": "TALK_JOHN_MAGA",
    "dynamic_line": "&[He beams proudly.] \n\n \"Make America Great Again! Voted for Trump in the 2nd election, after I saw his attitude on immigrants. While I'm good friends with Mexicans, them Chinamen have no place in the Great U S of A. Hell, they retaliated with all these mind-controlled cannibals and deadheads.\"",
    "responses": [
      { "text": "Oh, alright then.", "topic": "TALK_JOHN" },
      { "text": "Hell yeah brother.", "topic": "TALK_JOHN" },
      { "text": "What if I'm Chinese?.", "topic": "TALK_JOHN_MAGA_CHINA" },
      { "text": "[Leave] \"Sorry...\"", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ],
    "replace_built_in_responses": true
  },
  {
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "id": "TALK_JOHN_MAGA_CHINA",
    "dynamic_line": "&[He stares at you for a while. The tension in the air is thick as diesel.] \n\n[Suddenly, he breaks out laughing, barely even able to breath.] \n\n \"Oh, that's a good one, you're obviously no Chink. Besides, even if your parents were Chinese, you ain't part of this shit.\"",
    "responses": [
      { "text": "That's... Not what I expected.", "topic": "TALK_JOHN" },
      { "text": "[Leave] \"...\"", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ],
    "replace_built_in_responses": true
  }
]
